What do you say? I mean, this is
a very serious

18:33.546 --> 18:36.048 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
charge he's making, that the
process is crooked.

18:36.148 --> 18:39.652 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
REINCE PRIEBUS, Republican
National Committee
Chairman: Well, I don't know how
serious the

18:39.752 --> 18:41.487 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
