18:41.587 --> 18:45.624 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And I'm not sure how much is
rhetoric, and
-- but the truth is, is that the
process is

18:45.725 --> 18:51.197 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
