was only after
the results did we get a single
complaint

19:30.069 --> 19:30.669 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
about the process.

19:30.770 --> 19:32.538 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Right.

19:32.638 --> 19:34.407 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Well, let me read -- you're
familiar with
this, but let me read you what
Donald Trump

19:34.507 --> 19:37.810 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
