to win in Colorado, they changed
the system."

19:43.416 --> 19:46.786 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
And he said the people in
Colorado didn't
know that their votes were going
to be taken

19:46.886 --> 19:48.421 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
