19:48.521 --> 19:53.859 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
REINCE PRIEBUS: Well, and that
statement has
been debunked by many people.

19:53.959 --> 19:58.697 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Colorado had a convention the
