contests.

19:58.798 --> 20:03.903 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
In other words, there weren't
elections. It
was a straw poll that didn't
award any delegates

20:04.003 --> 20:08.774 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
