20:10.810 --> 20:16.749 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And they went to the straight-up
convention.
So -- and, By the way, 60,000
people competed

20:16.849 --> 20:23.389 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
in Colorado in the precinct
level contest.
Then those people moved to a
county contest.

20:23.489 --> 20:28.527 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Then those people moved to a
congressional
district contest. And then they
moved to a

20:28.627 --> 20:32.565 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
