participated.

20:32.665 --> 20:36.669 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
They had surrogates speaking. No
one along
the way said, hey, I don't
really like the

20:36.769 --> 20:39.438 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
