really like this
kind of system.

20:39.538 --> 20:40.506 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: But it is...

20:40.606 --> 20:42.408 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
REINCE PRIEBUS: And now, all of
a sudden...

20:42.508 --> 20:44.810 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: I was just going
to say, but
it is the case, if you look at
state after

20:44.910 --> 20:50.616 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
state after state, the process
is different
in virtually every one of the 50
states. It's

20:50.716 --> 20:52.618 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
