rules and they
vote for officers. It's a real
convention.

21:34.927 --> 21:39.665 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
It's not a four-day party. It's
just that
no one ever watches what happens
during the

21:39.765 --> 21:44.503 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
day at these conventions, when
rules are voted
on and there is actual business
that goes

21:44.603 --> 21:45.938 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
on.

21:46.038 --> 21:47.840 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
It's no different than when the
Boy Scouts
have a convention...

21:47.940 --> 21:49.808 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: But when...

21:49.909 --> 21:50.743 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
REINCE PRIEBUS: ... or when the
Kiwanis have
